description: With Guess What I'm Thinking, you can try to get inside Alexa's brain. Simply ask Alexa to start guess what and you will get 5 multiple choice questions to answer. This skill is just for fun...an amusing way to pass the time.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask guess what to start new game.
name: Guess What I'm Thinking
shortDescription: Try to guess what Alexa is thinking.
